Class CompositeResourceBundle

All Implemented Interfaces:
JoinableResourceBundle
public class CompositeResourceBundle
extends JoinableResourceBundleImpl

This class acts as a proxy for a group of bundles which are created independently but share a common id and act as a single bundle in runtime. It allows to join bundles which have different configuration, such as different posprocessing filters.

Author:
Jordi Hernández Sellés
